des:
Stay up to date on the latest information from our carrier partners at your convenience. With the Amwins Connect Underwriting Promos skill you can quickly hear the current promotions for all our California carriers. Simply tell Alexa the carrier name you are interested in.

Try saying things like:
“What are the Anthem promotions?”
“Tell me the Blue Shield promos”
“UnitedHealthcare”

Have a comment, suggestion, or question? Reach out to us at 866.570.5474 or visit us at www.amwinsconnect.com.
